41:04.610 --> 41:05.968
♪ Could barely tear ♪

41:05.978 --> 41:08.479
♪ My eyes away ♪

41:11.384 --> 41:16.920
♪ All you have is your fire ♪

41:19.250 --> 41:22.072
- You have to wait here.
- Where's my father?

41:22.728 --> 41:25.262
♪ Tame your demons ♪

41:26.966 --> 41:30.000
♪ But always keep 'em on a leash ♪

41:34.406 --> 41:35.498
♪ Mm... ♪

41:35.508 --> 41:37.508
MARSHALL: Conrad.

41:38.744 --> 41:40.090
Dad.

41:41.347 --> 41:43.642
♪ Mm... ♪

41:45.117 --> 41:46.617
I'm okay, son.

41:48.521 --> 41:50.579
I'm okay.

41:50.589 --> 41:54.116
♪ My senses fooled me ♪

41:54.126 --> 41:55.518
