41:55.528 --> 41:57.453
♪ Thought gasoline ♪

41:57.463 --> 41:59.422
♪ Was on my clothes ♪

41:59.432 --> 42:01.590
♪ When I was a man ♪

42:01.600 --> 42:04.802
♪ I thought it ended ♪

42:07.673 --> 42:11.642
♪ When I knew love's perfect ache ♪

42:12.278 --> 42:14.336
